title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 10/13 - Dean Evason, Bill Guerin, Vikes Bites
description: PA opens the show talking to Wild head coach Dean Evason about tonight's season opener against the Rangers, Wild GM Bill Guerin stops by the box to continue the conversation on the Wild, plus some Vikes Bites on our favorite purple & gold squad.
